 {\rm P}(|\bar X_n - 0|  \ge \varepsilon ) \le \frac{{{\rm Var}(\bar X_n )}}{{\varepsilon ^2 }} \to 0. 
 {\rm E}(|\bar X_n  - 0|^2 ) = {\rm Var}(\bar X_n ) \to 0. 
